CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1941, pg. 12 reads: "National Officers, Delegates And Visitors To Debs About Town Confab In Pittsburgh"...center, left to right; Ada Fisher, Washington; Dorothy Glenn, Cleveland...- Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Ada Fisher wearing fur coat, and Dorothy Glenn, posed in front of Loendi Club porch, for Debs About Town conference
